This is for you guys who are having a hard time installing jeppview:

1.  Install jeppview program 3.5
2.  Install cycle 01-2009 disk 1
         (If you don't have this cycle, you can         download it here in piratebay)
Full Worldwide : 207HF34080
VFR Europe    :  207HE34083
* The purpose of installing this update is for the site code to work (R00D-KCAB)
* Jeppview will ask for it after installing the cycle

3.  After installing the cycle and registered it..... you can now install the latest cycle.

Hope you guys understand this.
